The '''green-naped tanager''' ('''''Tangara fucosa''''') is a species of [[bird]] in the family [[Thraupidae]]. It is found in the [[Serranía del Darién]] and [[Serranía del Baudó]] ([[Colombia]] and [[Panama]]). It is threatened by [[habitat loss]].

